{
  "body" : "You are designing an expressive, dynamic sketch-style illustration.\n\nCONTENT BRIEF\n- Character: {{character}}\n- Action: {{action}}\n- Setting: {{setting}}\n- Style notes: {{style_notes}}\n\nSTYLE DIRECTION\n- Genre / medium: expressive hand-drawn sketch illustration\n- Composition: centered subject with balanced negative space, capturing motion and energy through layered strokes\n- Lens / camera: implied motion blur and depth through exaggerated lines and overlapping contours\n- Lighting: abstracted and implied through color shading with warm-to-cool tones\n- Color palette and grading: dual-tone complementary palette (orange and blue) with muted saturation, evoking dynamism and contrast\n- Texture / surface: rough and energetic pencil-like strokes with visible layering\n- Post-processing: no smoothing, retaining raw line texture and sketch-like imperfections\n- Mood: dynamic, energetic, raw, expressive\n- References: dynamic sketch illustration styles; dual-tone shading reminiscent of traditional pencil techniques\n\nDESIGN RULES\n- Aspect: 2:3 portrait (~1024×1536) suitable for editorial or poster illustration\n- Subject must dominate the composition, with motion captured through exaggerated linework\n- Background should remain minimal to emphasize the character and action\n\nAVOID\n- Overly clean or digital-looking lines\n- Excessive detail that detracts from motion\n- Busy or cluttered backgrounds\n- Flat or lifeless color applications\n- Lack of visible stroke energy\n\nAdditional constraints: {{extra}}\n\n——————\nCharacter: {{character}}\nAction: {{action}}\nSetting: {{setting}}\nStyle notes: {{style_notes}}\nExtra constraints: {{extra}}",
